title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 4PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday afternoon’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 4PM” game were:
7-6-4-6
(seven, six, four, six)
